ygData.messageBody:
When Squire Narl is around you will know it! He shouts across the entire
zone that he is looking for Altunic. The problem is I think that many
people in the zone will get there and kill him before you have a chance
because he is sooooo irritating.

From: Nichol, Adam [mailto:acnich@...]
Sent: Friday, June 18, 1999 2:58 PM
To: 'eqpaladin@onelist.com'
Subject: [eqpaladin] Squire Narl


From: "Nichol, Adam" <acnich@...>

Where is this guy?! I know I am suppose to look around the 3rd inn while in
East Commons but I have not seen him yet and it has been a long time
searching. Any clue as to how often he spawns? What level is he?

Aslan
